+# Pala Memory Core
+
+Local-first AI work memory for ChatGPT, Codex, files, reports, and backups.
+
+## What It Does
+
+Pala Memory Core captures important AI work during the day, stores it as durable local records, links it to projects, creates daily briefings, and prepares backup/report receipts.
+
+The MVP starts with reliable manual capture:
+
+```text
+python pala.py remember --title "Pala Memory Core idea" --text "Capture this work."
+python pala.py brief today
+python pala.py backup receipt
+python pala.py dashboard export
+python pala.py dashboard serve
+```
+
+## Core Idea
+
+| Layer | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| Capture | Save chat notes, Codex outputs, files, PDFs, screenshots, and links |
+| Memory | Store records as Markdown + JSON |
+| Project Link | Connect records to GitHub repos or local folders |
+| Report | Produce daily briefs and evidence reports |
+| Backup | Prepare local/GitHub/Drive backup receipts |
+| Dashboard | Show today's records, sources, projects, and backup state |
+
+## Repository Layout
+
+```text
+pala-memory-core/
+  README.md
+  AGENTS.md
+  pala.py
+  schema/
+    record.schema.json
+  dashboard/
+    index.html
+  docs/
+    commands.md
+  examples/
+    sample-record.json
+  data/
+    inbox/
+    records/
+    reports/
+    attachments/
+    backups/
+```
+
+## MVP Commands
+
+| Command | Status | Result |
+|---|---|---|
+| `remember` | v0.1 | Creates a Markdown + JSON memory record |
+| `brief today` | v0.1 | Creates a daily Markdown briefing |
+| `backup receipt` | v0.1 | Creates a local backup receipt |
+| `dashboard export` | v0.2 | Writes `dashboard/records.json` for the local panel |
+| `link project` | planned | Adds repo/folder references to a record |
+| `backup github` | planned | Publishes report package to knowledge bank |
+| `dashboard serve` | v0.3 | Starts local dashboard server |
+
+## Data Principles
+
+- Local-first by default
+- Human-readable Markdown records
+- JSON metadata for automation
+- SQLite or full-text search later
+- No secrets in published reports
+- Backup is evidence storage, not release approval
+
+## Related Repositories
+
+| Repo | Role |
+|---|---|
+| `trugurpala/hafizalar` | Work discipline and agent protocol |
+| `trugurpala/pala-os-bilgi-bankasi` | Reports, evidence, decisions |
+| `trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Product implementation |
