+# Backlog
+
+## Sprint 1: Local Core
+
+| Issue | Title | Outcome |
+|---|---|---|
+| `PMC-001` | Create local config file | User can set data path and knowledge-bank repo |
+| `PMC-002` | Add `remember` command | User can save Markdown + JSON memory records |
+| `PMC-003` | Add attachment copy and hash | PDFs/images/files are copied safely |
+| `PMC-004` | Add `brief today` command | Daily summary file is generated |
+| `PMC-005` | Add `backup receipt` command | Local backup receipt is generated |
+| `PMC-006` | Add `list` command | User can see recent records |
+| `PMC-007` | Add `show` command | User can inspect one record |
+| `PMC-008` | Add static dashboard data export | Dashboard can load `records.json` |
+| `PMC-008B` | Add local dashboard server | Dashboard can be opened from localhost |
+
+## Sprint 2: Project And Knowledge Bank
+
+| Issue | Title | Outcome |
+|---|---|---|
+| `PMC-009` | Add `link project` command | Existing records can be linked after capture |
+| `PMC-010` | Add report package generator | Implementation report package is prepared |
+| `PMC-011` | Add knowledge-bank folder convention | Reports land in predictable dated folders |
+| `PMC-012` | Add GitHub-ready manifest | Changed files and new files are listed |
+| `PMC-013` | Add raw patch attachment support | Patch/diff files can be included as evidence |
+
+## Sprint 3: Import And Dashboard
+
+| Issue | Title | Outcome |
+|---|---|---|
+| `PMC-014` | Add PDF/text import metadata | Imported files become searchable records |
+| `PMC-015` | Add ChatGPT export import plan | Official export path is documented and parsed |
+| `PMC-016` | Make dashboard read local JSON | Static preview becomes live local panel |
+| `PMC-017` | Add filters by source/project/tag | User can find records quickly |
+| `PMC-018` | Add daily briefing view | Dashboard shows today's summary |
+
+## Sprint 4: Backup And Connectors
+
+| Issue | Title | Outcome |
+|---|---|---|
+| `PMC-019` | Add GitHub backup connector | Reports can be published to configured repo |
+| `PMC-020` | Add Google Drive backup design | OAuth and upload flow is specified |
+| `PMC-021` | Add browser capture design | Playwright/Chrome capture is optional |
+| `PMC-022` | Add mobile share/import design | Phone capture uses share/export first |
+| `PMC-023` | Add secret redaction pass | Common secrets are filtered before backup |
+
+## Risk Register
+
+| Risk | Mitigation |
+|---|---|
+| ChatGPT live history access is limited | Start with manual capture and official export import |
+| Browser capture breaks when UI changes | Keep Playwright connector optional |
+| Mobile OS blocks background capture | Use share sheet/export flow |
+| Public GitHub leaks private data | Add explicit backup command and redaction checks |
+| Data grows too large | Add retention and archive policy |
