+# Commands
+
+## remember
+
+Creates a local memory record as Markdown + JSON.
+
+```text
+python pala.py remember --title "Idea" --text "Important note"
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--source codex` | Mark source as Codex |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-os-v4` | Link to a GitHub repo |
+| `--file path.pdf` | Attach a file |
+| `--decision "..."` | Add a decision |
+| `--task "..."` | Add an open task |
+| `--tag memory` | Add a tag |
+
+## brief today
+
+Creates a daily Markdown brief from today's records.
+
+```text
+python pala.py brief today
+```
+
+## backup receipt
+
+Creates a local backup receipt. This is the MVP placeholder before GitHub/Drive upload.
+
+```text
+python pala.py backup receipt
+```
+
+## dashboard export
+
+Writes today's local records to `dashboard/records.json` so the static dashboard can show real captured data.
+
+```text
+python pala.py dashboard export
+```
+
+## dashboard serve
+
+Starts a local dashboard server from the `dashboard/` folder.
+
+```text
+python pala.py dashboard serve
+```
+
+Default URL:
+
+```text
+http://127.0.0.1:8765
+```
+
+Custom host/port:
+
+```text
+python pala.py dashboard serve --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8787
+```
+
+## Planned
+
+| Command | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `pala link project` | Attach an existing record to a repo or folder |
+| `pala backup github` | Publish report package to `pala-os-bilgi-bankasi` |
+| `pala backup drive` | Upload selected artifacts to Google Drive |
+| `pala import chatgpt-export` | Import official ChatGPT data export |
