+# Connectors
+
+Pala Memory Core uses a staged connector model. The core stays local-first; connectors add capture, import, export, backup, or browsing capabilities.
+
+## Connector Table
+
+| Connector | Purpose | MVP Path | Risk |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| ChatGPT Desktop | Save important desktop conversations | Manual copy/import first | No guaranteed full live API |
+| ChatGPT Mobile | Save phone conversations | Share/export into inbox | Mobile OS restrictions |
+| ChatGPT Export | Import official export archive | Parse exported files | Export format can change |
+| Codex | Capture local coding sessions and outputs | Manual `remember` + report package | Needs user-approved capture scope |
+| GitHub | Publish reports and read repo context | Knowledge-bank report output | Secrets must be filtered |
+| Google Drive | Backup files and reports | Upload selected artifacts | OAuth setup required |
+| Browser/Playwright | Capture visible web context/screenshots | Optional screen/page capture | UI changes can break capture |
+| PDF/Documents | Import and summarize PDFs/docs | Attach file + metadata first | OCR/text extraction later |
+| Local Files | Attach screenshots, patches, markdown, notes | Copy into `data/attachments` | Large files need retention rules |
+| Obsidian/Logseq | Human-readable knowledge viewer | Markdown-compatible records | Optional user preference |
+
+## Connector Contract
+
+Every connector should produce or update a memory record with:
+
+| Field | Meaning |
+|---|---|
+| `source` | Where the memory came from |
+| `summary` | Human-readable short summary |
+| `attachments` | Files copied into local storage |
+| `project_refs` | Related repo/folder/project |
+| `evidence` | URL, file, screenshot, command, or note |
+| `backup_status` | Local/GitHub/Drive state |
+
+## Staging
+
+| Stage | Connectors |
+|---|---|
+| `v0.1` | Manual, Codex, Local Files |
+| `v0.2` | GitHub project links |
+| `v0.3` | Knowledge-bank report publish |
+| `v0.4` | PDF/Documents import |
+| `v0.5` | Browser/Playwright capture |
+| `v0.6` | Google Drive backup |
+| `v0.7` | ChatGPT export import |
+| `v0.8` | Mobile share/import flow |
+| `v1.0` | Unified dashboard and recovery |
+
+## Design Rule
+
+If a connector is fragile, keep it optional. The core should still work through manual capture and file import.
+
