+# Roadmap
+
+## Product Direction
+
+Pala Memory Core should become a local-first dashboard and CLI for saving, summarizing, linking, reporting, and backing up daily AI work.
+
+## Milestones
+
+| Milestone | Goal | Done When |
+|---|---|---|
+| `v0.1` | Manual memory capture | `remember`, `brief today`, `backup receipt` work locally |
+| `v0.2` | Project linking | Records can point to GitHub repos and local folders |
+| `v0.3` | Knowledge bank reports | Report package can be prepared for `pala-os-bilgi-bankasi` |
+| `v0.4` | Attachment imports | PDFs, screenshots, markdown, text files are copied and hashed |
+| `v0.5` | Live local dashboard | Dashboard reads exported local records from local server |
+| `v0.6` | GitHub backup | Reports can be published to a configured GitHub repo |
+| `v0.7` | Google Drive backup | Selected artifacts can be uploaded to Drive |
+| `v0.8` | ChatGPT export import | Official exports can be imported and indexed |
+| `v0.9` | Browser capture | Playwright/Chrome can capture visible pages/screenshots |
+| `v1.0` | Recovery workflow | Deleted/scattered work can be found through local records |
+
+## MVP Non-Goals
+
+- Fully automatic capture of every ChatGPT conversation
+- Mobile background monitoring
+- Secret scanning with perfect accuracy
+- Cloud-only storage
+- Replacing ChatGPT, Codex, GitHub, Drive, Obsidian, or Logseq
+
+## First Coding Tasks
+
+| Task | Description |
+|---|---|
+| Add config file | Store knowledge-bank repo, data path, and backup targets |
+| Add list command | Show recent records |
+| Add show command | Print one record |
+| Add project link command | Update `project_refs` after capture |
+| Add static dashboard data export | Generate `dashboard/records.json` |
+| Add local dashboard server | Serve `dashboard/` at `127.0.0.1` |
+| Add secret filter | Redact common API key patterns before backup |
